    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:1.1",
          "pli": "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. ",
          "en": "At Sāvatthī. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:1.2",
          "pli": "Tena kho pana samayena kokāliko bhikkhu ābādhiko hoti dukkhito bāḷhagilāno. ",
          "en": "Now at that time the mendicant Kokālika was sick, suffering, gravely ill. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:1.3",
          "pli": "Atha kho turū paccekabrahmā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena kokāliko bhikkhu tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā vehāsaṃ ṭhito kokālikaṃ bhikkhuṃ etadavoca: ",
          "en": "Then, late at night, the beautiful independent brahmā Tudu, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, went up to the mendicant Kokālika, and standing in the air he said to him, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:1.4",
          "pli": "“pasādehi, kokālika, sāriputtamoggallānesu cittaṃ. ",
          "en": "“Kokālika, have confidence in Sāriputta and Moggallāna, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:1.5",
          "pli": "Pesalā sāriputtamoggallānā”ti. ",
          "en": "they’re good monks.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:1.6",
          "pli": "“Kosi tvaṃ, āvuso”ti? ",
          "en": "“Who are you, reverend?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:1.7",
          "pli": "“Ahaṃ turū paccekabrahmā”ti. ",
          "en": "“I am Tudu the independent brahmā.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:1.8",
          "pli": "“Nanu tvaṃ, āvuso, bhagavatā anāgāmī byākato, atha kiñcarahi idhāgato? ",
          "en": "“Didn’t the Buddha declare you a non-returner? So what exactly are you doing back here? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:1.9",
          "pli": "Passa, yāvañca te idaṃ aparaddhan”ti. ",
          "en": "See how far you have strayed!” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:2.1",
          "pli": "“Purisassa hi jātassa, ",
          "en": "“A man is born "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:2.2",
          "pli": "kuṭhārī jāyate mukhe; ",
          "en": "with an axe in his mouth. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:2.3",
          "pli": "Yāya chindati attānaṃ, ",
          "en": "A fool cuts themselves with it "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:2.4",
          "pli": "bālo dubbhāsitaṃ bhaṇaṃ. ",
          "en": "when they say bad words. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:3.1",
          "pli": "Yo nindiyaṃ pasaṃsati, ",
          "en": "When you praise someone worthy of criticism, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:3.2",
          "pli": "Taṃ vā nindati yo pasaṃsiyo; ",
          "en": "or criticize someone worthy of praise, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:3.3",
          "pli": "Vicināti mukhena so kaliṃ, ",
          "en": "you choose bad luck with your own mouth: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:3.4",
          "pli": "Kalinā tena sukhaṃ na vindati. ",
          "en": "you’ll never find happiness that way. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:4.1",
          "pli": "Appamattako ayaṃ kali, ",
          "en": "Bad luck at dice is a trivial thing, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:4.2",
          "pli": "Yo akkhesu dhanaparājayo; ",
          "en": "if all you lose is your money "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:4.3",
          "pli": "Sabbassāpi sahāpi attanā, ",
          "en": "and all you own, even yourself. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:4.4",
          "pli": "Ayameva mahantataro kali; ",
          "en": "What’s really terrible luck "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:4.5",
          "pli": "Yo sugatesu manaṃ padosaye. ",
          "en": "is to hate the holy ones. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:5.1",
          "pli": "Sataṃ sahassānaṃ nirabbudānaṃ, ",
          "en": "For more than two quinquadecillion years, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:5.2",
          "pli": "Chattiṃsati pañca ca abbudāni; ",
          "en": "and another five quattuordecillion years, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:5.3",
          "pli": "Yamariyagarahī nirayaṃ upeti, ",
          "en": "a slanderer of noble ones goes to hell, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn6.9:5.4",
          "pli": "Vācaṃ manañca paṇidhāya pāpakan”ti. ",
          "en": "having aimed bad words and thoughts at them.”"
        }
      ],
